thread.title: Ryan Boal
thread.title_full: CDKey Warehouse reviewed by Ryan Boal

author: Ryan Boal
title: Ryan Boal
text: Decided to get myself a few steam codes off these guys, waited over a week to finally receive my codes. Only problem was that none of the codes worked at all and had already been claimed. Have sent numerous support tickets only to just be ignored, have asked for a refund but still no sign of wanting to fix the problem. Nothing but a scam these people are, don't buy from them and waste your money.
